# Day 6 – Dictionary Iteration 🔁

## What it does
Extends the Day 5 dictionary by iterating through
all key-value pairs using .items() and printing
them in a clean format.

## Tech Stack
- Python 3 (built-in only)

## How to run
python quicky.py

## What I learned
- Iterating dictionaries with .items()
- Unpacking key-value pairs in a for loop
- f-string formatting with dynamic keys and values

## Output
Prints each dictionary field on its own line
as "key: value".
